cueup-points-description: Cueup points can be used to remove the fee on gigs, thus increasing the payout.
Cueup point kan bruges til at fjerne gebyrer fra gigs og dermed øge fortjenesten.

no-gigs-description: You will get a notification when new gigs are available.

Login to see your gigs: Log ind for at se dine gigs.

description: All information is encrypted. We are using IBAN numbers to allow deals between countries. That way you can play gigs in foreign contries if you're traveling.
Alt information er krypteret. Vi bruger IBAN-nummer for at kunne tilbyde gigs i udlandet.
address-description: Enter the address of the person or business that the bank account is associated with.
Indtast adressen på den person eller forretning som bankkontoen er forbundet med.
IBAN-description: Your IBAN number can typically be found on your online bank, the banks mobile app or on your bank account statement.
Dit IBAN-nummer kan typisk findes i netbank, i bankens app eller på din kontooversigt.
terms: By clicking save, you agree to our terms and conditions, and stripes connect account agreement.
Ved at trykke gem, accepterer du vores betingelser, og stripes connect account agreement.

empty-page-message: Ser ud til at der ikke findes noget her.

Waiting on DJ's to make offers: Waiting on DJ's to make offers
The event is confirmed and payed: The event is confirmed and payed
site-description: Cueup is an online platform connecting DJs and event organizers - the easiest way for you to book a great DJ for your event.  Just tell us about your event, and within 1 day you will receive non-binding offers from DJs near you.

Cueup er en online platform der forbinder DJs og eventarrangører - den nemmeste måde at booke en fremragende DJ til dit event. Du skal blot fortælle os om dit event, og inden for 1 dag vil du modtage ikke-bindende tilbud fra lokale DJs.
removed-facebook: To protect our users privacy, we have removed facebook as a login option. If you previously logged in using facebook, create a new password by clicking FORGOT.
For at beskytte vores brugeres data, har vi fjernet facebook som login. Hvis du tidligere har brugt facebook som login, kan du oprette et nyt kodeord ved at trykke på GLEMT.
payment-succes-message: Your payment has been received, and you will receive a receipt on email.
Din betaling er modtaget, og du vil få en kvittering på din email.
